      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why im typing this. everything is just gone. the company, the funding, the reputation... i owe people money i cant ever pay back. i just keep thinking about my parents seeing me like this. the shame is actually physical. i feel like i'm just a walking mistake and everyone's better off if i just wasn't around to embarrass them.",
